title: What Collection Should We Add to the DAO Vault?
body:
Reasoning: In our previous Google Form DAO vote, our community narrowed DAO Vault choices down to Mutant Ape Yacht Club, CyberKongz, and The Doge Pound. This vote will serve to conclude which collection we'll be adding to the DAO Vault.

Mutant Ape Yacht Club: https://opensea.io/collection/mutant-ape-yacht-club
CyberKongz: https://opensea.io/collection/cyberkongz
The Doge Pound: https://opensea.io/collection/the-doge-pound

Timeline: We'll purchase an NFT from the winning collection approximately 24 hours after the conclusion of this vote.

Cost: The DAO will use DAO Wallet funds to purchase an NFT from the winning collection.
